item.title: CVE-2021-3661|2024-08-03T17:01:07.807Z -- hp%20inc. -- hp%20workstation%20bios
item.description: A potential security vulnerability has been identified in certain HP Workstation BIOS (UEFI firmware) which may allow arbitrary code execution. HP is releasing firmware mitigations for the potential vulnerability.
